---
title: Creamy Cashew Tofu with coriander and fragrant pilau rice
description: The crispy tofu in this dish is complemented perfectly by the sweet and nutty flavour of the creamy cashew sauce. Turmeric-infused rice acts as the aromatic backdrop to an undeniably vibrant dish.
